            <primitiveValues>
                <formulaTemplate>To cancel an open order on the Ndax mobile web version, follow these steps.

1.	Log in to your Ndax account.
2.	Tap the Ndax logo at the top left to open the menu.
3.	Select “Trade” from the menu.
4.	Tap the orders icon in the bottom right corner of the screen.
5.	Locate the open order you want to cancel.
6.	Tap the “X” icon next to that order.
7.	A confirmation message will appear at the top of the screen confirming the cancellation.</formulaTemplate>
